<h2 class="page-title">🏛️ Our World-Class Infrastructure</h2>
<p class="sub-title">Creating an environment where learning meets innovation and excellence.</p>

<div class="infra-container">
    <div class="infra-box">
        <h3>📚 Ultra-Modern Library</h3>
        <p>Our library is a treasure trove of knowledge, offering **10,000+ books, journals, research papers, and digital resources**. Equipped with **Wi-Fi, e-learning portals, and private study rooms**, the library fosters a rich learning environment.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="infra-box">
        <h3>💻 Hi-Tech Computer Labs</h3>
        <p>Our **cutting-edge computer labs** are equipped with **high-speed internet, advanced software tools, AI-driven research platforms, and coding environments** to help students stay ahead in technology.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="infra-box">
        <h3>🏋️‍♂️ Fitness & Sports Arena</h3>
        <p>We believe in a **healthy body and mind**. Our **sports complex includes a fully-equipped gym, indoor games, basketball & badminton courts, and a football ground**, encouraging students to stay active.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="infra-box">
        <h3>🎭 State-of-the-Art Auditorium</h3>
        <p>With a seating capacity of **500+ students**, our air-conditioned auditorium hosts **guest lectures, corporate events, cultural programs, and international conferences** with **world-class audiovisual facilities**.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="infra-box">
        <h3>🍽️ Hygienic Cafeteria & Dining</h3>
        <p>Our spacious **cafeteria** serves **nutritious, multi-cuisine food** in a clean and comfortable environment. The **24/7 food court** ensures students and faculty always have access to quality meals.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="infra-box">
        <h3>🏠 Comfortable Hostel Facilities</h3>
        <p>Separate **boys and girls hostels** with **24/7 security, high-speed internet, study rooms, and recreation areas** provide students a home-like atmosphere, ensuring safety and comfort.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="infra-box">
        <h3>🧪 Advanced Science & Research Labs</h3>
        <p>Our **research-driven science and innovation labs** are equipped with **modern instruments, AI-integrated learning modules, and collaboration spaces** for real-world problem-solving.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="infra-box">
        <h3>🚗 Smart Parking & Transport Facilities</h3>
        <p>With **ample parking space** and a **well-connected transportation system**, ASBM ensures easy access to campus. Our fleet of **college buses** covers multiple city routes for student convenience.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="infra-box">
        <h3>🏥 On-Campus Medical & Health Services</h3>
        <p>ASBM provides **24/7 medical assistance, emergency care, and wellness programs** with a fully functional **health center, ambulance services, and certified medical professionals**.</p>
    </div>
</div>

